<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='978350' id='t-978350'>and she was very nice to Randolph as well.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='982211' id='t-982211'>But Nico's the best reader I could hope for.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='986561' id='t-986561'>I would want anyone I was writing for</span>
